  "detailed_description": "<strong>Dungeon Rebound is a unique and innovative take on the classic arcade genre. Players will take control of a character in a fast-paced, action-packed adventure that blends role-playing elements with classic arcade-style gameplay.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440550/extras/642ebd3f512f3472096c4a94fc93e9e6.poster.avif?t=1696367048\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440550/extras/642ebd3f512f3472096c4a94fc93e9e6.webm?t=1696367048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440550/extras/642ebd3f512f3472096c4a94fc93e9e6.mp4?t=1696367048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Control a diverse cast of RPG characters, each with their own unique abilities and playstyle.</li></ul></strong>  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440550/extras/5d68bc91821b9e40d1b3b56101d926ba.poster.avif?t=1696367048\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440550/extras/5d68bc91821b9e40d1b3b56101d926ba.webm?t=1696367048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440550/extras/5d68bc91821b9e40d1b3b56101d926ba.mp4?t=1696367048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Harness the power of magic, melee combat, ranged attacks, and more to dominate the court.</li></ul> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440550/extras/ef9fbccdf375c1d2971a276fd0eb8feb.poster.avif?t=1696367048\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440550/extras/ef9fbccdf375c1d2971a276fd0eb8feb.webm?t=1696367048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440550/extras/ef9fbccdf375c1d2971a276fd0eb8feb.mp4?t=1696367048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Level up your characters, unlock new skills, and customize your playstyle to match your strategic preferences.</li></ul></strong>",
